<lb n="1064b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1064b0701">含理者也三爻。能敷者也十翼。若闕彖<note n="1064001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">繫＝&CB00747;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1064001"><lem wit="【大】">繫</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&CB00747;</rdg></app>龜
